{"tid":1535397,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大律師公會聲明　批評警方執法用過份武力　太子站不合理打市民","createTime":"2019-09-03T10:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T12:57:37.000Z","uid":8659,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"09138e59714be3606e045296fce6f35b82c45263","tid":1535397,"uid":8659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:47:51.000Z","msg":"【編按：大律師公會發聲明，指近日有證據顯示部分警員執法偏離以往標準，在太子站不合理以暴力對待市民。】<br />\n<br />\n警隊基本的職責是保護市民的生命，安全及福祉，維護治安及把罪犯繩之於法，使其得到公平的司法程序處理。上述是法治精神的重要一環。<br />\n<br />\n可是，近日有證據顯示部分警員執法時已偏離警隊一貫高質素執法的標準。在過去數月，大量傳媒拍攝到的視像及影片顯示警務人員在執行驅散及拘捕示威者行動時使用過份武力，包括不合理地施發催淚彈（包括在港鐵站內）及近距離向人群肩膊以上位置開槍。警方於拘捕時毆打被捕者已被廣泛拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n於上星期六晚在港鐵太子站內拍攝到的視像，顯示防暴警察在無合理的情況下以暴力對待市民，包括向月台上及在車廂內的乘客以無差別的方式施放胡椒噴霧及以警棍毆打，而其後警員離開港鐵車廂時並沒有作出任何拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n香港大律師公會的會員在向被捕人士提供法律支援時曾在警署遭受多番無理阻撓，令被捕人士未能適時接觸律師及得到法律代表的協助，被捕人士亦投訴在拘留期間受到虐待，導致身體受傷需要送院或接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n除上述外，警方亦作出其他違反警察通例規定的行為，如執勤的警員沒有在制服上展示任何可以辨識其身份的記認，從而製造一種「不用問責」及「能逃過監察」的意識。警方其後所作出的解釋，例如指特別戰術小隊的制服上沒有空位作上述展示，亦實屬牽強，不能服眾。<br />\n<br />\n無論面對任何困難及挑釁，警察仍應保持克制及以符合警察通例的要求行事。以上的要求至為重要。法律要求警隊以專業的操守執勤，只可以使用與當時情況合適的最低武力執法。<br />\n大律師公會譴責任何警隊或警務人員濫用權力的情況。警務人員作為被賦予公權及擁有各種殺傷力不等的武器的紀律部隊，無論在面對市民大眾或示威者時，都不能使用過份或不必要的武力。以上所述的情況已經削弱公眾對警隊的信心。至今，只有成立一個獨立及全面的調查委員會，找出事實真相，才可挽回社會對警隊的信心。<br />\n<br />\n香港大律師公會<br />\n<br />\n2019 年 9 月 3 日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E7%94%A8%E9%81%8E%E4%BB%BD%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B-%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E6%89%93%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%2581%258E%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B-%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%2F&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDYDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=fb96abc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%2581%258E%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B-%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%2F&h=da1391bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E7%94%A8%E9%81%8E%E4%BB%BD%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B-%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E6%89%93%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91/</a>"},{"pid":"4794cd9a76524b4cddb21294aa25ba44b1f48b29","tid":1535397,"uid":123991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:48:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3403695ac1e565be3ebeb68b2fa80829689e5d66","tid":1535397,"uid":286897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocEEoB8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocEEoB8.jpg&h=b5b1706e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B7pwZau.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB7pwZau.jpg&h=7daeb6e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13931afa40018d61679a7568ada6fe4e575c5aab","tid":1535397,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a62aa089589569cb63f61ab18a43f64a86efe52","tid":1535397,"uid":233651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:48:43.000Z","msg":"直線抽擊"},{"pid":"8e39e354cd84ce0e05494af4efa28a148a2548a7","tid":1535397,"uid":104699,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:49:21.000Z","msg":"六月以來，支持勇武抗爭既人已經越黎越多，但點解仲未有恐怖份子受到應有制裁?恐怖份子每戰必勝零傷亡，下次就更加出力施暴，反正打傷打殘打死香城人唔洗負責。<br />\n<br />\n唔係勇武手足唔夠勇，亦唔係左膠手足太過膠，係無法可依，勇武唔可以放手全力殺賊，左膠過唔到心理關口怕錯殺無辜，亦無人想負上非法行為既罪名。<br />\n<br />\n所以當務之急，係要立即組織成立香城自治臨時立法委員會，用三罷集會既時間草擬並進行公投，草創香城自治臨時大法典，係恐怖份子完全摧毀香城法治既呢段時期，成為香城市民執法自保既重要依據。<br />\n<br />\n例如: 香城自治臨時大法典第一章第一條:<br />\nA)任何違反戰爭法、國際人權公約或意圖非法挪用香城外匯儲備人士，立即遞奪香城市民資格。<br />\nB)任何人士持械襲擊香城市民，即視為恐怖份子，市民可以最高武力反擊格殺或將其制服，並免除一切法律責任。<br />\nC)任何被制服之恐怖份子，經香城臨時法庭審判，一經定罪，可立即就地執行死刑，以香城自由意志之名義宣判其死罪，以人道立場給予一分鐘口述遺言，以漫浸清水之黑色衣服包裹其頭部十分鐘，犯人死亡後遺體以傳統火葬儀式處理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以香城市民逐漸醒覺既趨勢，好快就會出現生擒一個落單既恐怖份子既事件，如果無法可依，最後都係無功而還，恐怖份子只會越黎越恐怖，依法處決先可以摧毀其士氣，香城市民上前線先會安全。<br />\n<br />\nLaw 友們請行動!"},{"pid":"cae8bc9cd5778e4cbdb3ffe2367ae4fe636aaba3","tid":1535397,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:49:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a7917d33b76ff9ac5eeb9d0258a50440d01bcabb","tid":1535397,"uid":137217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3403695ac1e565be3ebeb68b2fa80829689e5d66","tid":1535397,"uid":286897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocEEoB8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocEEoB8.jpg&h=b5b1706e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B7pwZau.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB7pwZau.jpg&h=7daeb6e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mvOxJEA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmvOxJEA.jpg&h=8a346096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係祈禱集會<br />\n唔係普通集會<br />\n我地好守法唔會非法集結的"},{"pid":"88c9c5f5937b53f1fcf659c9a42591af2ab55aec","tid":1535397,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:50:43.000Z","msg":"直線屌柒黑警"},{"pid":"b21037f74cfc68328ddf176ff465d9a45a584de3","tid":1535397,"uid":128178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:51:06.000Z","msg":"今時今日既警隊，佢唔出席獨立調查委員會都吹佢唔脹"},{"pid":"d2cd919b65caec5efb77e7686dac808500cdd379","tid":1535397,"uid":279236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:51:31.000Z","msg":"Law友終來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33aa54b818b4e217ab7833c03ae9ab8f23b6deed","tid":1535397,"uid":83989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:51:41.000Z","msg":"ご署名をお願いします！<br />\n香港における政府当局による強権的な動きをけ